-- BP Slumps to 14-Year Low as Cost of Gulf Spill Operation Tops $2 Billion
-- Stephen Cunningham
-- 2010-06-25T08:24:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/bp-slumps-to-14-year-low-as-cost-of-gulf-spill-operation-tops-2-billion.html

          
          
             BP Plc slumped to a 14-year low
after the company said the cost of cleaning up the Gulf of
Mexico oil spill rose to $2.35 billion.  
          
          


  


        